[MAKOTO]
I'm here Takashi. Talk to me!

00:21:42.469 --> 00:21:43.678 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:21:45.555 --> 00:21:48.850 position:50% align:center
If for some reason I don't
make it, then listen.

00:21:48.933 --> 00:21:51.603 position:50% align:center
Promise me...
that you will lead...

00:21:51.686 --> 00:21:54.439 position:50% align:center
...the G-Boys in my place.

00:21:54.522 --> 00:21:58.693 position:50% align:center
And don't you dare tell me...
that it's a bother.

00:22:00.779 --> 00:22:02.739 position:50% align:center
I'm counting on you.

00:22:06.201 --> 00:22:08.286 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO]
Takashi!

00:22:09.788 --> 00:22:12.457 position:50% align:center
[RIOT POLICE gasp]

00:22:12.540 --> 00:22:14.876 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO]
By the time the cops arrived,

00:22:14.959 --> 00:22:17.045 position:50% align:center
the entire place was deserted.

00:22:22.175 --> 00:22:26.179 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO] The Red Angels turned
Isogai over to the authorities.

00:22:26.262 --> 00:22:28.473 position:50% align:center
I doubt we'll see
him for a while.

00:22:29.724 --> 00:22:31.559 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO]
Mitsuki was unharmed.

00:22:31.643 --> 00:22:34.479 position:50% align:center
Seems they were going to
frame him for killing me

00:22:34.562 --> 00:22:38.942 position:50% align:center
before tying any loose ends.
That's why he was still alive.

00:22:40.443 --> 00:22:42.737 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO]
Kyouichi's army disbanded.

00:22:45.198 --> 00:22:46.366 position:50% align:center
[KYOUICHI]
My folks left me a house

00:22:46.449 --> 00:22:49.285 position:50% align:center
on the other side of
the Yamanote Line.

00:22:49.369 --> 00:22:52.288 position:50% align:center
I've decided to hole up there.

00:22:52.372 --> 00:22:55.041 position:50% align:center
It's best if I make myself
scarce around these parts

00:22:55.125 --> 00:22:56.751 position:50% align:center
for the time being.

00:22:59.504 --> 00:23:01.923 position:50% align:center
Oh, and look after
my family, will you?

00:23:03.883 --> 00:23:07.512 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO] Takashi pulled through.
It was a minor wound.

00:23:07.595 --> 00:23:09.431 position:50% align:center
He'll be out of
the hospital soon.

00:23:11.224 --> 00:23:13.935 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO]
Ikebukuro is the best.

00:23:14.019 --> 00:23:17.230 position:50% align:center
It's in the northwest
part of downtown Tokyo.

00:23:17.313 --> 00:23:20.525 position:50% align:center
Full of skyscrapers and
department stores.

00:23:20.608 --> 00:23:24.988 position:50% align:center
It's in these streets where
we live our lives in peace.

00:23:25.071 --> 00:23:27.615 position:50% align:center
We're about love and harmony.

00:23:27.699 --> 00:23:30.410 position:50% align:center
It's the friendliest
place on earth.

00:23:30.493 --> 00:23:34.456 position:50% align:center
Yep. That's why
Ikebukuro's the best!

00:23:36.708 --> 00:23:38.335 position:50% align:center
[MALE CLIENT A]
Makoto Majima?

00:23:39.502 --> 00:23:42.005 position:50% align:center
[MALE CLIENT A] I was hoping
you had time to chat.

00:23:42.088 --> 00:23:43.506 position:50% align:center
[chuckles]